The files in this directory are originally released by Sun Microsystems, Inc. 
The source code has been modified by simplifying the ADPCM algorithm to increase 
running speed.

Here, the quantizer scale factor, y(k), is determined by "unlocked" factor
yu(k) only. The factor yl(k) and speed-contral factor al(k) are ignored.

--Chengxiang Lu (CMU   lu+@cs.cmu.edu)

  Nov. 11, 1994
